title: Hack Your Brain
itunes:title: Hack Your Brain
description:
Episode 152 - Your brain is a 2 million year old piece of machinery. It is not designed to keep you happy or make sure you are successful, it is designed to keep you safe. That being said, there are things you need to learn about your brain in order to "hack" it so that you can get past your fears and create the future you desire.
